name: Tetragonus
description:
Mimicking the Acanthocereus tetragonus, the barbed wire texture of the ring creates a unique finishing touch to any outfit. Worn as a midi ring or a normal ring, this statement piece is versatile. Because this ring is one-of-a-kind, there is only one in stock in size 4 and made out of chrome-cobalt. 

To know more about our home-made jewelry and the hand-crafting process, please read the About page.

name: Paradoxa
description:
This collar necklace is made out of chrome-cobalt, a non-precious metal that will not rust or fade. It is a one-of-a-kind necklace that symbolizes the beauty in the Rhipsalis paradoxa. 

To know more about our home-made jewelry and the hand-crafting process, please read the About page.

name: Encelia
description:
Modeled after a one and a half inch piece of lace fabric, the pendant was created by the form of metal casting. This one of a kind metal lace necklace is made out of non-precious metal, chrome-cobalt. 
Because this necklace is unique, there is only one in stock.
